</div>

<section id="home" class="section">
    <img src="/images/avatar.jpg" class="avatar" />

    <h1>Leoth</h1>

    <p class="quote">
        A small digital corner on the internet.
    </p>

    <div class="links">
        <a href="#">Facebook</a>
